---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
import { SITE_NAME, PHONE_NUMBER } from '../../utils/constants';
import { generateServiceSchema } from '../../utils/schema';

const schema = generateServiceSchema({
  name: 'Professional Stump Grinding Service',
  description: 'Complete stump grinding and stump removal in Birmingham, AL. Eliminate stumps 12-18 inches below ground.',
  provider: SITE_NAME
});

const pageTitle = 'Professional Stump Grinding in Birmingham, AL | Complete Removal';
const pageDescription = 'Expert stump grinding service removing stumps 12-18 inches below ground. Prevent regrowth and reclaim your yard space. Free quotes.';
---

<Base title={pageTitle} description={pageDescription}>
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(schema)} />

  <!-- Hero Image -->
  <section class="bg-white py-0">
    <img src="/images/services/stump-grinding-hero.png" alt="Professional stump grinder operator with Rayco stump grinding equipment at residential property" class="w-full h-96 object-cover object-center" />
  </section>

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-green-700 to-green-900 text-white py-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">Professional Stump Grinding Services</h1>
          <p class="text-xl text-green-100 mb-8">
            Complete stump removal with grinding 12-18 inches below ground. Reclaim your yard space without hazards or regrowth concerns.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
            <a
              href={`tel:${PHONE_NUMBER}`}
              class="bg-white text-green-700 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-bold hover:bg-gray-100 transition text-center"
            >
              Call Now for Free Quote
            </a>
            <a
              href="/contact"
              class="border-2 border-white text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-bold hover:bg-white hover:text-green-700 transition text-center"
            >
              Request Online
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-green-600 rounded-lg p-8">
          <div class="text-5xl font-bold mb-2">12-18"</div>
          <p class="text-green-100">Ground-level grinding prevents regrowth and future root problems</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Grind Stumps -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-12 text-center">Why You Need Professional Stump Grinding</h2>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-8 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">❌ Prevents Regrowth</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Grinding 12-18 inches below ground eliminates the entire root system, preventing sprouting and regrowth that would otherwise continue for years. A tree stump can live for decades and sprout new growth continuously. Professional grinding destroys these roots permanently, so you'll never deal with persistent sucker growth from that stump again.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-8 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">🪲 Stops Pest Infestation</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Decomposing stumps attract termites, carpenter ants, and other harmful wood-eating insects that can then spread to your home. These pests can travel through underground root connections toward your foundation and wooden structures. Grinding the stump removes this pest highway and protects your home from dangerous insect infestations.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-8 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">🏠 Improves Safety</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Stumps create serious trip hazards, especially for children, elderly visitors, and pets who may not see them in tall grass. Removing the stump eliminates these obstacles, making your yard safer and more usable. You also reduce liability risks from injuries that could occur on your property.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-8 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">📈 Increases Property Value</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">A clean, stump-free yard dramatically improves curb appeal and can noticeably increase your home's market value. Potential buyers want yards that are ready to use, not yards cluttered with remnants of removed trees. A professionally restored yard signals excellent property maintenance.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-8 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">🌳 Reclaims Yard Space</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">After grinding, the area is level and ready for immediate use. Plant a new tree, create a garden bed, expand your patio, or simply enjoy more open yard space. The grinding process also produces mulch that can be used for landscaping around your property.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-8 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">💰 Cost-Effective</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Professional stump grinding is one of the most affordable ways to completely eliminate stumps. It's far cheaper than chemical treatments, expensive delayed removal years later, or trying to dig out roots manually. Professional grinding delivers complete stump elimination at a reasonable price.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Stump Grinding Facts -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-20 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-12 text-center">Stump Grinding Facts</h2>

      <div class="bg-white p-12 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-green-600">
        <ul class="space-y-4 text-gray-700">
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-green-600 font-bold">✓</span>
            <span>A tree stump can live for decades and continue sprouting new growth</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-green-600 font-bold">✓</span>
            <span>Termites can travel from a stump to your home through buried roots</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-green-600 font-bold">✓</span>
            <span>Our grinders reach 12-18 inches below ground, destroying the entire root system</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-green-600 font-bold">✓</span>
            <span>The resulting mulch can be used in landscaping or removed</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-green-600 font-bold">✓</span>
            <span>Professional grinding takes 1-4 hours depending on stump size</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Our Process -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-12 text-center">Our Stump Grinding Process</h2>

      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="flex gap-6">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-center h-12 w-12 rounded-md bg-green-600 text-white font-bold">1</div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Inspection & Preparation</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2">We conduct a thorough assessment of the stump, identifying underground obstacles including buried rocks, concrete, or utility lines that could damage equipment. This inspection is critical—hitting a utility line or hidden concrete could create hazards. We mark the work area, clear surrounding debris, and plan the optimal grinding approach for safety and efficiency.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex gap-6">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-center h-12 w-12 rounded-md bg-green-600 text-white font-bold">2</div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Professional Grinding</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2">Our powerful, specialized grinding equipment systematically removes the stump and roots 12-18 inches below ground level, destroying the entire root system. We operate the grinder with precision to ensure complete removal while controlling debris and dust. The grinding process typically takes 1-4 hours depending on stump size and hardness of the wood.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex gap-6">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-center h-12 w-12 rounded-md bg-green-600 text-white font-bold">3</div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Site Restoration</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2">The resulting mulch can remain on-site for landscaping purposes or be completely removed—your choice. We level the area, fill the hole with clean fill material, and leave your yard neat and ready for immediate use. The restored area can be landscaped, planted, or used for any purpose you prefer.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="bg-green-900 text-white py-16 md:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Get Your Stumps Ground Today</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-green-100 mb-8">
        Eliminate stumps and reclaim your yard with professional stump grinding. Get a free quote.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a
          href={`tel:${PHONE_NUMBER}`}
          class="bg-white text-green-900 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-bold hover:bg-gray-100 transition text-lg"
        >
          Call {PHONE_NUMBER}
        </a>
        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="border-2 border-white text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-bold hover:bg-white hover:text-green-900 transition text-lg"
        >
          Request Free Quote
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
